{"tid":1313706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過朱sir感受！！！","createTime":"2019-07-14T01:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:31:17.000Z","uid":3177,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36f28417a18b5ba033afc78d830c1bd64323888c","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:01:33.000Z","msg":"<em>2019年1月21日，終審法院認為朱經緯沒有合理解釋，拒絕朱經緯的上訴許可申請。同日，警察隊員佐級協會再次向公務員事務局局長羅智光發公開信，促請局方推動「侮辱公職人員罪」立法。上訴方認為當時朱經緯只為執法，問心無愧。終院頒下的判詞指《公安條例》僅容許警方執勤時使用所需的武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">同意原審裁判官所言當時根本沒任何理據使朱真誠地相信可行使武</span>力，縱然法庭同情朱當時所面對的是非常令人遺憾（highly regrettable）的處境，<span style=\"color: red;\">但法庭絕不能姑息對市民無理施以武力的行為</span>。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">朱蛇：<span style=\"color: red;\">你班友打到興高采烈，棍棍有力！<br />\n點解！點解我要入冊！點解個天咁唔公平！！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">朱蛇示意圖</span></strong></em><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lau7d83.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flau7d83.gif&h=7d87493a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77f79c289163182c8faedb8f5212d6cc3c72f5f7","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">朱蛇： 連休班警都爽過我！！點解！！</span>"},{"pid":"3eb733206e9ee05f99d513d337c08c79bbd5743d","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6a1c7b5eec8a5276872966694cdd7f953d34a7","tid":1313706,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a78c3072ce9e3979da2fbf75bc08732e1c209c4","tid":1313706,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:24:51.000Z","msg":"黑警唔理朱蛇<br />\n黑警可恥"},{"pid":"5a3a2f502ee28879ff031dd8773b5b16c3b2a123","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"朱蛇應該都支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得同班警賊講：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">出得黎行 預左要還<br />\nyou are well paid for it!<br />\n<br />\n若然未報！時候就到！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3110ad9214632cc72f7a631040c93f6d7608f2c","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6221e49052fafbdb1b3bca2352ad57860294b8d7","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"小心"},{"pid":"262f96b92367191f52a58cdcc3e0b61b88581125","tid":1313706,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51aaf50f046d476322b27e7a9a131fcd8619ff5f","tid":1313706,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"203548735445749b9aea91e5cbfea302b4f0c0ca","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"各位今日小心"},{"pid":"9a3aeace34a891c4a54ef45bfadc3dda52fd0a84","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b29935688ca12817d59a915c17dec4ffb21fed","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">若然未報 時候未到</span></strong></span><br />\n<em>拘捕與檢控<br />\n42日後正式被捕<br />\n2014年11月26日，警方在對彌敦道佔領區進行清場後，七名警員在事隔42日後終於被拘捕。網民認為是為平息清場引起的民憤有關。不過，網民對七人只被控以「襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪」，而非因其公職人員身份而控以「酷刑罪」甚為不滿，因「酷刑罪」最高刑罰是終身監禁，而現時控罪最高刑罰只是監禁三年，程度明顯有別，認為是故意放生。<br />\n<br />\n一年後終被檢控<br />\n律政司在「七警」被捕後多次稱要徵詢不同的法律意見，外界均認為屬拖延之舉。至2015年10月，事件屆滿一週年的日子，互聯網頻傳律政司終建議香港警方將檢控七警的消息。<br />\n<br />\n但在10月15日早上，卻率先傳出被毆的曾健超收到警方預約拘捕的消息。終於在當天中午，警方發言人表示，涉案七名警員已被正式落案起訴，各被控一項有意圖導致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪，其中一人再被控普通襲擊罪，全部獲准保釋外出，下周一東區法院提堂。根據《警隊條例》，總督察或以下職級警務人員停職時，仍有機會獲支半薪，直至被定罪為止。</em>"},{"pid":"521b5ed09054cb024da4a9cc228d56b071cd1651","tid":1313706,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/091502-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F091502-1.jpg&h=1ffcfbd4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}